data.description: Sellers may be willing to offer rate-buydown credit with acceptable offer! Welcome to your dream home nestled in Wescott Plantation! Freshly painted and ready for it's new owners!! This beautiful home boasts an expansive 3142 sq ft of living space that perfectly blends comfort and practicality. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a light-filled, airy floor plan that effortlessly connects the living spaces, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. As you walk through you will notice the tall ceilings, wood plank ceramic tile flooring, and a beautiful wide arched entry into the elegant, open floor plan. The heart of the home is thoughtfully designed for both family gatherings and entertaining, featuring a formal dining area with tray ceilings and a cozy breakfast nook for those casualmornings. In the gourmet kitchen you will notice the crisp white cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances that overlook the kitchen peninsula into the spacious family room. Beyond the family room, you will find a downstairs guest bedroom that could also serve as a music room or private home office. You will also find a powder room adjacent to the guest room as well as a downstairs laundry.  The large upstairs primary suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, sitting just off of the stairs with French door entry. The primary suite features ample closet space and a private en-suite bathroom. The upstairs loft provides an additional versatile space that can be tailored to your needs, whether it's a playroom, home office, or home theater. Off of the loft, you will find 3 additional large bedrooms that share a full bath. Situated on a wooded lot within a cul-de-sac, the outdoor space offers privacy and tranquility.  This exceptional home is not just a destination, but a part of the coveted Wescott Plantation community. Centrally located and within the desirable DD2 school district, you'll enjoy easy access to local amenities, shopping, dining, and entertainment.
